62
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:24,160
Stop it.

63
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:24,840
Stop it.

64
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:26,400
Ziqing, you really misunderstood.

65
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,280
Stop it, my ass!

66
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:30,290
How dare you hit him?

67
00:03:30,720 --> 00:03:31,079
What?

68
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:32,120
