71
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:34,600
Ziqing.

72
00:03:34,760 --> 00:03:35,560
Both of you...

73
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:36,200
Get lost.

74
00:03:49,720 --> 00:03:50,280
I admit

75
