92
00:04:25,960 --> 00:04:27,220
Business is business.

93
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:29,440
Just give me enough compensation.

94
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:30,300
Compensation?

95
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:31,700
Please don't, Lan.

96
00:04:32,280 --> 00:04:32,840
Still talking so much nonsense?

97
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:33,400
Lan.

98
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:34,300
I'm sorry, Lan.

99
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:35,360
Don't.

100
