123
00:05:36,880 --> 00:05:37,520
Nothing.

124
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,520
Young Master, Miss Chen.

125
00:05:43,520 --> 00:05:44,650
I'll leave you to it.

126
00:05:47,159 --> 00:05:47,720
Ziqing.

127
00:05:48,520 --> 00:05:50,760
Did you and Boss Ye get hurt yesterday?

128
00:05:51,760 --> 00:05:52,920
Are you worried about me

129
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,360
