130
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:57,000
Of course I'm worried about you.

131
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,610
That's more like it.

132
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:00,320
I'm fine.

133
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:01,240
I got it.

134
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:03,090
Someone framed you yesterday.

135
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,360
I misunderstood you.

136
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:07,060
