141
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,200
Got it?

142
00:06:15,200 --> 00:06:15,680
Okay.

143
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:20,290
Try the nutritious meal I made for you.

144
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:30,600
Thank you, Ziqing.

145
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:33,180
By the way, Haoran.

146
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,080
