167
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:26,450
How about it?

168
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:28,000
The problem that bothered us

169
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,730
was easily solved by me, right?

170
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:31,240
Ziqing.

171
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:33,600
Actually, Boss Ye also recommended many

172
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:34,560
