174
00:07:36,440 --> 00:07:37,960
No need to consider others.

175
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:40,600
Vincent has been very popular these past two years.

176
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:41,800
And he has won several

177
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:44,610
championships in international competitions.

178
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:46,850
He's not suitable to be a teammate.

179
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:49,880
