180
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:02,930
Sorry, Captain.

181
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,650
In the second round,

182
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:06,160
I got fifth place.

183
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:07,120
Dead last.

184
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:11,360
Don't.

185
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:12,360
Don't.

186
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:13,360
All right.

187
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:16,040
My team

188
00:08:16,400 --> 00:08:17,930
