189
00:08:18,280 --> 00:08:20,200
I've only heard some news about him.

190
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:21,860
I wouldn't say I know him well.

191
00:08:22,280 --> 00:08:22,840
Anyway,

192
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,680
