195
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:44,330
Captain.

196
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,560
Vincent Shi.

197
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:50,400
Asian GT Series.

198
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:51,680
Dragon Country Grand Prix.

199
00:08:51,680 --> 00:08:54,160
The rookie in the F1 International Grand Prix,

200
00:08:54,160 --> 00:08:55,690
