213
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:26,370
Captain.

214
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:29,330
About what happened back then,

215
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:30,640
I am sorry.

216
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:32,560
All these years, I have been...

217
00:09:32,560 --> 00:09:33,090
Alright.

218
00:09:34,400 --> 00:09:36,480
